data.description: Presenting an exquisite luxury residence in the prestigious Estancia At Cibolo Canyons gated community, nestled in the tranquility of a cul-de-sac at 24342 Mateo Ridge, San Antonio, TX 78261. This magnificent 2-story home boasts 5 bedrooms, 5.5 baths, spanning 3788 sq ft on a generous 0.376-acre lot.    The gourmet kitchen is a culinary masterpiece, featuring top-of-the-line stainless steel appliances, a gas cooktop, and dual ovens - perfect for entertaining large gatherings. Two expansive islands and a spacious dining area provide ample space for family and friends to gather.    The living room is a haven of comfort, adorned with a 3D wall applique and a fireplace, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere for cozy winter nights. Ascend to the second story, where you'll discover a bedroom and a stunning loft that can seamlessly transform into a media room, game room, or a combination of both.    This residence is a true gem, offering a perfect blend of elegance and functionality. Don't miss the opportunity to witness the unparalleled luxury and comfort of 24342 Mateo Ridge. Schedule your viewing today.
